<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Mba taomy aho e FFPM439</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mba taomy aho e,
 Ry Tompo ô !
 Ho tonga zanakao
 Madio am-po,
 Mba taomy aho e,
 Ho tia Anao tokoa !
 Ny fo atolotro
 Mba raisonao.

[V2]
 Tariho aho e,
 Ry Jeso ô !
 Aza ilaozanao,
 Fa be manjo.
 Trotroy an-tratranao
 Ny ondrikelinao,
 Ka ento mody izao
 Ilay nania.

[V3]
 Diovy aho e,
 Fanahy ô !
 Diniho sy hazavao,
 Ny toetro.
 Diovy aho e,
 Ny fo ovay ho vao,
 Ka ny fanahiko
 Onenonao.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>439</hymn_number>
<author>R. Lowry</author>
</song>